  "description": {
    "zh": "巨大的声响已经不会让我措手不及了，但我不能对竞技场观众说同样的话。然而他们并不讨厌在战斗中使用爆炸物，而这不仅仅是因为我们的安全标准……我猜他们喜欢肾上腺素飙升的感觉，毕竟他们物有所值，这可不是骗局，哥们儿。\n\n现在你可能在想我为什么要告诉你这些，嗯……这就是原因，我需要一些数据，特别是关于爆炸物的。既然我现在心情不错，我会给你一些自由，好吧？所以你可以用任何你想用的东西，手榴弹、发射器、GP-25，你说了算。其实你知道吗？让我给你一些备用装备，反正这里也没人用，所以交给真正需要的人才是明智之举，拿去吧。你知道该怎么做，捍卫者。",
    "en": "Loud noises don't catch me off guard anymore, but I can't say the same for the arena audience. Yet they don't hate it when explosives are used in the battles, and that's not just because of our safety-standards... I'm guessing they love the adrenaline rush, they are getting what they are paying for after all, this ain't a scam buddy.\n\nNow you're likely wondering why I am even telling you this, well... Here's why, I need some data, on explosives specifically. Since I'm in a good mood right now, I will give you some freedom here, alright? So you can use whatever you want, grenades, launchers, GP-25s, it's your call. Actually you know what? Let me give you some spare equipment, nobody here uses it anyway so it would only make sense to give it to someone who actually needs it, here you go. You know what to do champion."
  },
